📊 Project Overview
System Optimizer is a cross-platform desktop application built with Tauri and React that provides AI-powered system optimization suggestions to improve boot time and overall performance.

Technology Stack
Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Zustand (state management)
Backend: Tauri 2.x (Rust), sysinfo crate for system monitoring
Platform Support: macOS and Windows
